{"items": [{"shortCode": "DZdZ5RvuEWV", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DZdZ5RvuEWV/", "caption": "Lies you absolutely cannot lie about on your resume otherwise you will lose your job offer. \n\nI talk about this and more in my latest YouTube video. Comment 'YouTube' for a direct link to the channel or check out my link in bio", "timestamp": "2026-06-11T20:45:44.000Z", "videoDuration": 61.013, "videoPlayCount": 1370, "videoViewCount": 524, "likesCount": 31, "commentsCount": 2, "displayUrl": "https://instagram.fhsv1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/722859134_18105089686965847_6909328965901589983_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&_nc_ht=instagram.fhsv1-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gHqqtBFYwsgJoI0qO_-cgcmxk74PMBEZU_2nBXAjoDU1bBrdIPUydAfEjr5DDZV_kg&_nc_ohc=JtPYk4pnDOoQ7kNvwGyq0V1&_nc_gid=QIm-OI8v8JhqHF4l37u6bQ&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af-KlULdtfCQME4ksaawj6-MZFuWq4kK1N-QX26YDqA51A&oe=6A324639&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQO9tP_vRInqg2AnWrLpf5WB42EImcHje1foLhjpccekdGq4QdB8dJTd5zBciAOAe_agAXz4bu1GQyCpRH1qdPiPifyaG---CvZgnlg.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=103&vs=1918161548898449_1566615493&_nc_%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=bfa059a320&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af8o0-NAudbnVUyDghqxZmEr9ZRe62aVXlOfoaj-FwhmQQ&oe=6A2E5EE1&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "farahsharghi", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "27183360904663798"}, "ownerUsername": "farahsharghi", "ownerFullName": "Farah Sharghi | Career Coach", "transcript": "I'm going to walk you through what you absolutely cannot lie about on your resume. And these lies will get your offer pulled the moment they're caught, and most of them get caught. Your education, your degree, whether you actually graduated. Legally claiming you have one when you don't counts as falsifying the application. The companies you worked at and the dates that you worked there. And if your dates don't line up to what your old employer reports, that's the end of the conversation. Whether you were fired or laid off. Getting fired isn't a deal-breaker. Lying about it is the deal-breaker. Skills and softwares you don't actually know how to use. Especially if you're at a senior level. Foreign language proficiency. There's a real chance an interviewer is going to start speaking it to you in your interview. So only list languages that you're actually fluent in. And finally, a fabricated job title or management responsibility. There's a difference between translating and inventing. Calling yourself CEO when you weren't is inventing. Those are the things you cannot lie about."}, {"shortCode": "DZcVy1Zusi2", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DZcVy1Zusi2/", "caption": "Resumes are simple, they're a document that demonstrates your business value to a business. That's it!", "timestamp": "2026-06-11T10:49:38.000Z", "videoDuration": 33.707, "videoPlayCount": 683, "videoViewCount": 217, "likesCount": 26, "commentsCount": 1, "displayUrl": "https://instagram.fshd1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/722664240_18105038386965847_2932034826276094266_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&_nc_ht=instagram.fshd1-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFzxWV399DPNQzebC5Dm3FU6NnHB3Sonuu9NIfLhWG5GWjLHgLQxhKSZ0YDsCiVPek&_nc_ohc=Q4giQDk5ONoQ7kNvwHTSHN8&_nc_gid=tIwlHmAjRb1r3-c50_84rA&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af_6isodE5RHMoAunxEpg8hFyomCTQQZSIYXeNlgJYPzMA&oe=6A3264B9&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-sea1-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQOKoG6NOUTqre8b2qHCRICz65hT6aW0p62WK93Q7cwhBwMLftBFV7R5gjw8L4OWg7DIPx4VtXp1BSrCu8TuHri6ER4yjrmOnqM2f8Y.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=104&vs=1881502662540568_369234407&_nc_vs=HBksFQIYUmlnX3hwdl9yZWVsc19wZXJtYW5lbnRfc3JfcHJvZC81QzRDN0Y1Q0QzNjk4NzhGMTc4MDkwODM0NUIxNkY5OV92aWRlb19kYXNoaW5pdC5tcDQVAALIARIAFQIYUWlnX3hwdl9wbGFjZW1lbnRfcGVybWFuZW50X3YyLzMzNEM4QjY1RENCQkQ5OEI1NTJGQ0M1N0I2QUIzMDkxX2F1ZGlvX2Rhc2hpbml0Lm1wNBUCAsgBEgAoABgAGwAVAAAm2uXr%2F8SY%2FwQVAigCQzMsF0BA2ZmZmZmaGBJkYXNoX2Jhc2VsaW5lXzFfdjERAHX%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=c1412c827d&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af8NvTFdtEq-p7bErj0gQfvXbogGg2xELX6LPKqkyOPgow&oe=6A2E4AA3&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "farahsharghi", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "27606793732278772"}, "ownerUsername": "farahsharghi", "ownerFullName": "Farah Sharghi | Career Coach", "transcript": "What your resume is there to demonstrate is the business value of your labor. It's not a to-do list. Yeah, those are tasks, but what are the results of the things that you've done? Right now, I am hiring and I've been looking at a lot of resumes and a lot of it's just to-do lists. Also, the work that they've done, the most recent roles that they've done are not aligned to what I'm hiring for. And I'm being very clear in my job description exactly what it is that I'm hiring for. It demonstrates to the other party, can you communicate your labor value for this job to the hiring team?"}, {"shortCode": "DZSgc4DM6_2", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DZSgc4DM6_2/", "caption": "You're not a pick me, don't act like one! Its all about alignment", "timestamp": "2026-06-07T15:10:33.000Z", "videoDuration": 46.933, "videoPlayCount": 940, "videoViewCount": 299, "likesCount": 36, "commentsCount": 2, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-atl3-3.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/718099380_18104654119965847_6321421280359982306_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-atl3-3.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gHlTB3blHBLpuV4lkhtWk3_As7m6UKbQz2CvpXD7962Rn6hCteptwp2H5v4oE8cqDI&_nc_ohc=5dETob3txfMQ7kNvwE6-E59&_nc_gid=oEGqB6EyF49GC-nw63n-uQ&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af9z2MHe2AEPiiA-STuqM9ur7x3bIsAOmiz_77jAFtYwDQ&oe=6A32462B&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-atl3-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQPbEOBtZbNWxdq4ApStLmAZBWArxuVFUN8Z9y5m6vfNWBX0zGvEpEzU8eVsVJEq3iLpX3BRBT-X-SBY0QPcLPpVK1WV0V7m_usLfr0.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=106&vs=2134099844049127_4153188761&_nc_%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=714fcc3769&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af_6a5aaZTqqKyitlCXvKiK6-MMurwSz2nvjdTWDaSm0Dg&oe=6A2E4AFC&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "farahsharghi", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "36234369776207338"}, "ownerUsername": "farahsharghi", "ownerFullName": "Farah Sharghi | Career Coach"}, {"shortCode": "DY-HFLaxF9X", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DY-HFLaxF9X/", "caption": "STAR vs CAR vs HERO. This is how senior leaders answer questions", "timestamp": "2026-05-30T17:05:40.000Z", "videoDuration": 57.024, "videoPlayCount": 476, "videoViewCount": 108, "likesCount": 9, "commentsCount": 2, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-lga3-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/710978895_18103841959965847_1450536168532128600_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gHRQ5dxGImbhg_Z8_c7HPqt8Mpnto7uTPojcqGWXEeN6nGIE9HWK0jSpmNFi6zGlcg&_nc_ohc=KgpCTT4bcWUQ7kNvwEUbzUL&_nc_gid=5sNGNjkikOLB6Vnxn-r6Og&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af_jkX2pH4Gym57BrRH35XL5yDcrPGpi_N4cwNW_SgtqZg&oe=6A324CB6&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-msp1-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQOZktbVhZKOa8rh7i5x-V_akfxZ21qePPP0fcsXssNZXkcpwfnEm8ErK9paTLAfMYWSzzT8P_SWD-IGeI-pzjnbhpQEOeuOtzDGccQ.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=104&vs=4455270228135181_544760346&_nc_vs=HBksFQIYUmlnX3hwdl9yZWVsc19wZXJtYW5lbnRfc3JfcHJvZC81MjQzMzNDQzU3RDhDMDNEMEE2MTE1OEY4NDQ2OEM5RF92aWRlb19kYXNoaW5pdC5tcDQVAALIARIAFQIYUWlnX3hwdl9wbGFjZW1lbnRfcGVybWFuZW50X3YyL0U3NEJCMzdEMUE2NTQ0MkUyRTQzQUM0M0Y2ODJCQjgwX2F1ZGlvX2Rhc2hpbml0Lm1wNBUCAsgBEgAoABgAGwAVAAAmst%2FIs8bEzQMVAigCQzMsF0BMgvGp%2B%2BdtGBJkYXNoX2Jhc2VsaW5lXzFfdjERAHX%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=b754792f8b&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af98bQuq3oWUfQSF-VDcWLN-1XBX3eYqxSjsanBnbVodLA&oe=6A2E69BF&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "farahsharghi", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "27548799424737422"}, "ownerUsername": "farahsharghi", "ownerFullName": "Farah Sharghi | Career Coach", "transcript": "Here's a star answer. The situation had too many false positives in fraud detection. My task was to improve accuracy. The action I took was to rebuild the model with LightGBM. The result was $6 million in savings and 20% fewer manual reviews. Here's a car answer. The context was too many false positives. My action was to rebuild the pipeline with LightGBM. The result was $6 million in savings and 20% fewer manual reviews. Now, here's the hero answer. We cut fraud losses by $6 million a year and reduced manual reviews by 20%. This mattered because false positives were frustrating customers and wasting support time. We considered role-based filters, but they flagged too many legitimate users, so I built the pipeline with LightGBM and rolled it out across three regions. Now it sounds like a leader driving outcomes, not just a technician explaining steps."}, {"shortCode": "DYw7Sa7MZhQ", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYw7Sa7MZhQ/", "caption": "HERO in action. The STAR interview framework is great, but people usually spend too much time explaining the situation when they should be getting straight to the point.\n\nWatch the full video on my YouTube channel", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T14:12:10.000Z", "videoDuration": 50.325, "videoPlayCount": 653, "videoViewCount": 169, "likesCount": 16, "commentsCount": 0, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-dfw5-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/706198451_18103317709965847_2084496495369147086_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-dfw5-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFJgsuQ_Z9CHZX0UWvpqQaQrRex1pyvsi5Y-iYJQDdCBhRDfwza6TgEdHk-SkRu14E&_nc_ohc=XkT_jnPjIhwQ7kNvwFGEhfL&_nc_gid=x-wsUw0Qr71F7WR9EDdlgA&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af_HjbCWurUL5ls4RgEAec_PtJ5j3i2wZ3TkYuWkaumxPw&oe=6A323D97&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-atl3-2.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQPXAgIa1U08g2qi2KI97vCp-7jkr8M-NiAF7r5rKrE9fxUOkOYPky6vPBbuOUiyzt6FVXfCPQYC2zNITHarBrHbQW3wrp7xpgWJ-Xk.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=102&vs=1179425760948361_1664293754&_nc_vs=HBksFQIYUmlnX3hwdl9yZWVsc19wZXJtYW5lbnRfc3JfcHJvZC9GNTRDNDdFRDQwQzZCMDVDOEJBMTkxOUE3NzY5QjJBQ192aWRlb19kYXNoaW5pdC5tcDQVAALIARIAFQIYUWlnX3hwdl9wbGFjZW1lbnRfcGVybWFuZW50X3YyLzQwNEYxNEJEMzFDODhDNThCRjJCNzlBMjRDN0QyOEIwX2F1ZGlvX2Rhc2hpbml0Lm1wNBUCAsgBEgAoABgAGwAVAAAm3oCe29%2BszQgVAigCQzMsF0BJKHKwIMScGBJkYXNoX2Jhc2VsaW5lXzFfdjERAHX%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=2b95a21c0c&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af8M8ThJlbQCqZI99iRwfh0rW05vMwkC32WFcY1Sj9w-gA&oe=6A2E6F39&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "farahsharghi", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "26392656917079279"}, "ownerUsername": "farahsharghi", "ownerFullName": "Farah Sharghi | Career Coach", "transcript": "So let's talk about the hero framework. Hero stands for H, headline, start with the outcome, which is one sentence that's going to grab the attention of the interviewer. E is effect. This is why it mattered. What business user or product problem did it solve? R stands for rationale. What options did you consider? Why did you make the decision that you made? This shows judgment. O stands for operations. Finally, what you or your team actually did. So you can talk about the method, the tool, or the execution. This way your interviewer hears the impact immediately. Then you show you understand context and trade-offs, and you prove you can execute. When you move up the corporate ladder, you're going to be expected to think and act more strategically."}, {"shortCode": "DYf595_uegq", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYf595_uegq/", "caption": "STAR is great but you end up getting stuck in the situation for too long and lose people's attention.\n\nTo learn more about how to use the HERO method comment 'YouTube' and I'll send you a link to watch more.", "timestamp": "2026-05-18T23:32:52.000Z", "videoDuration": 45.291, "videoPlayCount": 660, "videoViewCount": 149, "likesCount": 18, "commentsCount": 2, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-mia3-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/702677190_18102645313965847_130331095769017488_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-mia3-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gE_yvKlPqdSLa98cpgcfftB5br0lzyt_TEWuqymqx1N_AToaJb0A9HuNrgwuYwVA24&_nc_ohc=MywLeuWgrFEQ7kNvwG6wGUA&_nc_gid=g3oOVeKWoHCNenH5L_UVHg&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af_81Thl-po_UnKBD8Uz7v6FmA5tdwsCZel54vVKh1xU4w&oe=6A32485C&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-mia3-3.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQMfazsLD0oiTwZn71OaNN7gDn1P-UYpe9IGuFKxGDJuS1zaEGvRWKjuf1itEyHCpcZ1EWfIpFxCroITH5U6Ng3M76XpCRIEn9sfkh0.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=109&vs=4435135120063627_1740693509&_nc_vs=HBksFQIYUmlnX3hwdl9yZWVsc19wZXJtYW5lbnRfc3JfcHJvZC80NDRBOTVFRDcxQjc4RTdFREVCRTQwMTcxMDdGOTVCNV92aWRlb19kYXNoaW5pdC5tcDQVAALIARIAFQIYUWlnX3hwdl9wbGFjZW1lbnRfcGVybWFuZW50X3YyLzlENDIxMDM2M0FDRjQzRkZCNjUxNEQ3NDE0RDlERUEzX2F1ZGlvX2Rhc2hpbml0Lm1wNBUCAsgBEgAoABgAGwAVAAAm4KeW6M%2BL0wQVAigCQzMsF0BGo5WBBiTdGBJkYXNoX2Jhc2VsaW5lXzFfdjERAHX%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=111227bdc0&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af8CXLYwGMIrBAybwJTd120VkDmdykwSRRC3aqwTurb32w&oe=6A2E4E15&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "farahsharghi", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "27529527116652007"}, "ownerUsername": "farahsharghi", "ownerFullName": "Farah Sharghi | Career Coach"}, {"shortCode": "DYa67-bJs3x", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYa67-bJs3x/", "caption": "Think the STAR method is the best interview formula? Think again. \n\nAfter years of creating content I realized that I could turn that knowledge into a new formula that has helped people get real offers from their interviews.\n\nWant to learn the HERO method? Comment 'YouTube' for a link to my YouTube page", "timestamp": "2026-05-17T01:04:49.000Z", "videoDuration": 39.125, "videoPlayCount": 1241, "videoViewCount": 402, "likesCount": 29, "commentsCount": 8, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-dfw5-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/696666611_18102443293965847_6429722765719410523_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-dfw5-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEjlJTMwdaXDJrriXq-_KsItwF2p2oi_j9muCpCuGw03y1yUVqD9ic8RtfD2Me81Sw&_nc_ohc=jzuqi9kFE7EQ7kNvwFtjmr4&_nc_gid=QUwgtq-UTZ49E_WB9lI5rQ&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af93_aeyI83pJdBpHHxO8AGQYwUBq2W-bLf3wKDEcGD_gA&oe=6A326A84&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://instagram.fosu3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQNqhwMg3oWb4FkJpzDtP-cJDu-UC6YM9seVb5sXvrFFz8iU7nxJ33nyA9OXnism_kVmrEf5tqS1hi7cLH13y_M7w_cbC-HLlnx6ZgA.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=109&vs=2179155866252706_1670464898&_nc_vs=HBksFQIYUmlnX3hwdl9yZWVsc19wZXJtYW5lbnRfc3JfcHJvZC9FMTQxRUZCQzM1NDEzOUZDQUY0RDM0M0M5NTE5QzNCNV92aWRlb19kYXNoaW5pdC5tcDQVAALIARIAFQIYUWlnX3hwdl9wbGFjZW1lbnRfcGVybWFuZW50X3YyL0U1NDFGRTlEM0FGRUE0NUY1QjVFQjUwMzc0MzgzQ0EzX2F1ZGlvX2Rhc2hpbml0Lm1wNBUCAsgBEgAoABgAGwAVAAAmkPL%2FtYG%2FiwUVAigCQzMsF0BDjXCj1wo9GBJkYXNoX2Jhc2VsaW5lXzFfdjERAHX%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=c75ae426a2&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af-KvHfiwl4mrIpaEs7Ozc7WAlLQzuwRwu0bOsxRwYzlLA&oe=6A2E6D11&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "farahsharghi", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "27637195995870068"}, "ownerUsername": "farahsharghi", "ownerFullName": "Farah Sharghi | Career Coach", "transcript": "Most people answer interview questions the wrong way. You've probably done this before. You start with all of the background, add a ton of context, and by the time you finally get the result, the interviewer already looks bored. If you've prepared for interviews before, you've probably used the STAR method, which stands for Situation, Task, Action, and Result, or the CAR method, which stands for Context, Action, Result. Now these are useful because they give your answer structure, so it's easier for the listener to follow. The problem with STAR and CAR is that they're chronological. STAR buries the impact at the end. HERO puts the impact up front."}]}